        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "So by the time we finalize the sprint, there's already a good idea of like, okay, this is how much time I was putting in like in week two to review a blog post.",
