        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "So like we specifically like just use like a different color so that the PMMs know like, okay, I need to like just go scroll to this section, read this specific part to make.",
