        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "sure that the SpecterOps, like solutions are being represented accurately and I also wanted to show you how we've been like so far when we're still generating the content, how we've been like implementing SEVS feedback, just to kind of give you an idea of the process and what it looks like on our end.",
