        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "But when, one of SEVS first pieces of feedback that he gave to us, like on the very first blog that we delivered was like, we have this white paper that we would like for you to use in the content generation process.",
