        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "We would like for you to reference it.",
            "timestamp": "00:05:55"
        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "So, we downloaded it and then.",
            "timestamp": "00:05:56"
        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "We kind of summarized the key points and we uploaded it as like a completely custom artifact so that whenever we are talking about like these topics, like identities at rest and identities in transit, it has, it can pull from these pieces of information that we provided in the white paper and it automatically like incorporates them into the article draft.",
            "timestamp": "00:06:00"
        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "So when it's writing the article, it can pull from this artifact and we can do this for like there's really not, I'm trying to be careful to say like no limit, obviously there are limits, but in terms of like the feedback that we get from product managers, whether it's we need to add more product mentions or we need to highlight specific benefits and kind of downplay other like some other information.",
            "timestamp": "00:06:23"
        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "These are all things that we can build like custom",
            "timestamp": "00:06:56"
        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "Some artifacts for, they get called during the article generation process.",
