        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "So we have like your agentic article pipeline here.",
            "timestamp": "00:07:04"
        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "And these are all like, we can just like incorporate it into these steps so that when it's generating the draft, it's calling like these different artifacts during that process.",
            "timestamp": "00:07:09"
        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "And it really is like super custom.",
            "timestamp": "00:07:21"
        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "And the best thing about it is that we don't need developers to do this.",
            "timestamp": "00:07:23"
        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "Like our content managers who are writing your content, they are able to edit the underlying pipeline and they can like just kind of play around and like test different approaches.",
            "timestamp": "00:07:27"
        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aida Kne\u017eevi\u0107",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aida@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "So just wanted to kind of throw that out there is that this is, you know, our goal is to kind of like not have product people just like spending a crazy amount of time, like reading all of this.",
            "timestamp": "00:07:39"
        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Meshach Cisero",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "mcisero@specterops.io"
            },
            "text": "Yeah.",
